.TH LIBRETRANSLATE-GUI 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "LibreTranslate GUI Manual"
.SH NAME
libretranslate-gui - Translation assistant using LibreTranslate
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B libretranslate-gui
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBlibretranslate-gui\fR is a GTK4/Adwaita translation assistant powered by LibreTranslate/Lingva. Features include live translation, auto-populated language selectors, batch translation, PO/TS file translation suggestions, configurable server support, API key authentication, translation history, and clipboard integration.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/libretranslate-gui/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/libretranslate-gui/
Cached data.
